The specialty about this entire group is the unexpected, they have been known to go in the craziest direction Musically and have it work. they're not afraid of using different producer from other countries and they also are not afraid to try something different and test those Waters sort of speak. This Song Is Banging, The Choreography is Sick, Ten is just dripping with Swag in this Video actually they all are. But he added a little more Flavor. author: @Necroherz
text:
But why was Jaehyun's "Baggy, baggy, baggy, baggy, baggy, baggy jeans" part so sexual... I want hear it again on a loop 👀🔥.. Also in the actual MV the most babygirl there was Mark and then Taeyong. Now in the performance was definitely you Jae hahah. I love the fluidity of Ten, man, he's so flexible is like a man of water. Mark was the perfect choice for those stylistic raps, that "YEAH BOYYYY!!!" will be forever iconic . Taeyong's sharpness and precision is flawless but also his lightness makes everything look easy on him, every move in every beat. Doyoungie is one of our main vocalist and i appreciate his efforts dancing so much, our bunny did it perfectly i'm so proud 🥺

Man i can't be more proud of my neos, even of SM Ent. which is not surprising i mean i love-hate this agency for many reasons but in terms of creativity and production, music and musically you're my number one always. Baggy Jeans was def in all the aspects the right decision. This performance was exquisite and well done, thank you so much 😭
